      <talk_answer link_index="n013_cleric_tomas-1-c" mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>龙的追随者?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>$牧师托马斯$<BR>曾经大家都以为杰克是个非常出色的牧师... 谁会想到他会成为<FONT color=#a82424>龙的追随者</FONT>了呢，真是悲剧啊。</html>]]></talk_question>
